From 1c6c0eb55ca65c460351e3b7dd040685451ae765 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Lokesh B V <Lokesh.BV@Arm.com>
Date: Mon, 23 Sep 2024 05:18:43 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 69/78] Platform/Sgi: define PCD for generic timer base address

The generic timer and watchdog timer control base on the RD-V3-R1
platform is different than those on the other platforms supported by
SgiPkg. So in order to reuse the existing GTDT ACPI table for all the
supported platforms, introduce and use PCD to provide the base
addresses for watchdog and generic timers.

TODO: Update other platforms...

Signed-off-by: Lokesh B V <Lokesh.BV@Arm.com>
Change-Id: I2012625051c290011c536af36ca798211d88b336
